
How to test
- RAW capture
	mplayer tv:///dev/video0 -tv driver=v4l2

- MJPEG capture
	mplayer tv:///dev/video0 -tv driver=v4l2:outfmt=mjpeg
	two test for both Dcim path

- MJPEG play
	ffmpeg -i test.avi -vcodec mjpeg -an -f v4l2 /dev/video0

	mplayer vo_zr/vo_zr2 does not compile and is a dead end

- Does MPEG is doable ?


